_std_deduction.long_name: Standard Deduction for income from Salary
_std_deduction.description: This amount is deducted from salary to compute taxable incomee.
_std_deduction.itr_ref: Section 16(ia) of the Income Tax Act

_rate1.description: The lowest tax rate, applied to the portion of taxable income below tax bracket 1.

_tbrk1.description: Taxable income below this threshold is taxed at tax rate 1.

_rate2.description: The second lowest tax rate, applied to the portion of taxable income below tax bracket 2 and above tax bracket 1.

_tbrk2.description: Income below this threshold and above tax bracket 1 is taxed at tax rate 2.

_rate3.description: The third lowest tax rate, applied to the portion of taxable income below tax bracket 3 and above tax bracket 2.

_tbrk3.description: Income below this threshold and above tax bracket 2 is taxed at tax rate 3.

_rate4.description: The fourth lowest tax rate, applied to the portion of taxable income below tax bracket 4 and above tax bracket 3.

_tbrk4.description: Income below this threshold and above tax bracket 3 is taxed at tax rate 4.

_ST_CG_RATE1.description: Rate at which 111A (STCG on shares units on which where STT paid) is taxed

_ST_CG_RATE2.description: Rate at which 115AD (STCG for FIIs on securities where STT not paid) is taxed

_LT_CG_RATE2.description: Rate at which 112 (LTCG on Others) is taxed

_rebate_thd.description: Income below this threshold is eligible for the rebate.

_rebate_ceiling.description: this is the ceiling for rebate u/s 87A

_surcharge_rate.long_name: rate at which surcharge is levied
_surcharge_rate.description: rate applied to tax liability if income is above a threshold

_surcharge_thd.long_name: income threshold for levy of surcharge

_cit_surcharge_rate.long_name: rate at which surcharge is levied for companies

_cit_surcharge_thd.long_name: income threshold for levy of surcharge for companies
_cit_surcharge_thd.description: income threshold for surcharge for companies

_cess_rate.long_name: rate at which cess is levied
_cess_rate.description: cess applied to sum of tax and surcharge

_cit_rate.long_name: rate at which corporates are taxed
